dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "British statute miles".
Shows topography, drainage, settlement boundaries of the tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
Appears in Lucas's A general atlas containing distinct maps of all the known countries in the world. Baltimore, 1823.
